name: TD Active U.S. Enhanced Dividend CAD Hedged ETF
longDescription: TD Active U.S. Enhanced Dividend CAD Hedged ETF seeks to earn income and generate moderate capital growth. The investing primarily in, or gaining exposure to, dividend-paying equity securities of issuers located in the United States, hedged to the Canadian dollar. The ETF may also invest in derivatives to enhance total return.
fulldescription: TD Active U.S. Enhanced Dividend CAD Hedged ETF seeks to earn income and generate moderate capital growth. The investing primarily in, or gaining exposure to, dividend-paying equity securities of issuers located in the United States, hedged to the Canadian dollar. The ETF may also invest in derivatives to enhance total return. In addition, the ETF may invest in other exchange-traded funds, including those managed by TDAM.
